</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BDB1745FFF8FFF1FF411F6FFC79DC7E" blockId="17.[151,1437,726,1257]" box="[151,900,834,861]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
<taxonomicName id="4C646CC6FFF8FFF1FF411F6FFD52DC7E" authority=": Radoman (1983)" authorityName="Radoman" authorityYear="1983" box="[151,687,834,861]" class="Gastropoda" family="Hydrobiidae" genus="Sarajana" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Mollusca" rank="subSpecies" species="apfelbecki" subSpecies="driniana">
<emphasis id="B910CB57FFF8FFF1FF411F6FFE22DC7E" box="[151,479,834,861]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Sarajana apfelbecki driniana</emphasis>
: 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF56AB4FFF8FFF1FE381F6EFD52DC7E" author="Radoman, P." box="[494,687,834,860]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" refId="ref53872" refString="Radoman, P. (1983) Hydrobioidea a superfamily of Prosobranchia. Sistematics. Vol. 57. Serbian Academy of Sciences and Arts, Belgrade, 256 pp." type="book" year="1983">Radoman (1983)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF56AB4FFF8FFF1FD6C1F6EFC7CDC7E" author="Jovanovic, B." box="[698,897,834,860]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" pagination="207 - 273" refId="ref48240" refString="Jovanovic, B. (1991) Katalog zbirke Hydrobioidea Pavla Radomana. Glasnik Prirodnjackog muzeja u Beogradu B, 46, 207 - 273. [in Serbian]" type="journal article" year="1991">Jovanović (1991)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BDB1745FFF8FFF1FF111F4AFC2FDC87" blockId="17.[151,1437,726,1257]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
<emphasis id="B910CB57FFF8FFF1FF111F4AFEA6DCA2" bold="true" box="[199,347,870,896]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Morphology</emphasis>
. Minute snails. Conical shell is up to 0.8 mm high. Aperture is rounded or angulated at the top, umbilicus is slit like. For more details see 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF56AB4FFF8FFF1FDA71FA6FCA2DC86" author="Radoman, P." box="[625,863,906,932]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" refId="ref53872" refString="Radoman, P. (1983) Hydrobioidea a superfamily of Prosobranchia. Sistematics. Vol. 57. Serbian Academy of Sciences and Arts, Belgrade, 256 pp." type="book" year="1983">Radoman (1983: 104</bibRefCitation>
, fig. 116).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C37E44CEFFF8FFF1FF111F82FDD9DA76" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="8BDB1745FFF8FFF1FF111F82FCF8DB33" blockId="17.[151,1437,726,1257]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
<emphasis id="B910CB57FFF8FFF1FF111F82FE0EDCEA" bold="true" box="[199,499,942,968]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Distribution and ecology</emphasis>
. Western Balkan endemic species. 
<typeStatus id="54DFA9E7FFF8FFF1FC5C1F83FC3FDCEB" box="[906,962,943,969]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Type</typeStatus>
locality is spring in the Kaoštica Village (Višegrad Municipality, BiH). In 
<collectingCountry id="F37357D5FFF8FFF1FDC21FFEFDA1DCCE" box="[532,604,978,1004]" name="Serbia" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Serbia</collectingCountry>
this snail was recorded from two small springs near the Perućac Stream (
<collectingRegion id="49A0D9A7FFF8FFF1FF491FDAFED2DB32" box="[159,303,1014,1040]" country="Serbia" name="Bajina Basta" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Bajina Bašta</collectingRegion>
Municipality, Tara Mtn., western 
<collectingCountry id="F37357D5FFF8FFF1FD7A1FDAFD04DB33" box="[684,761,1014,1041]" name="Serbia" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Serbia</collectingCountry>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BDB1745FFF8FFF1FF111836FA95DBCB" blockId="17.[151,1437,726,1257]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
<emphasis id="B910CB57FFF8FFF1FF111836FE81DB16" bold="true" box="[199,380,1050,1076]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Other remarks</emphasis>
. The species was assigned by Radoman to the monotypic genus, closely related to 
<taxonomicName id="4C646CC6FFF8FFF1FAEF1836FF2ADB7A" authorityName="A. J. Wagner" authorityYear="1928" class="Gastropoda" family="Hydrobiidae" genus="Belgrandiella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B910CB57FFF8FFF1FAEF1836FF2ADB7A" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Belgrandiella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Later, the distinctness of the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C646CC6FFF8FFF1FD551813FD17DB7B" authorityName="Radoman" authorityYear="1975" box="[643,746,1087,1113]" class="Gastropoda" family="Hydrobiidae" genus="Sarajana" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B910CB57FFF8FFF1FD551813FD17DB7B" box="[643,746,1087,1113]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Sarajana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was questioned, and 
<taxonomicName id="4C646CC6FFF8FFF1FC331813FB8BDB7A" baseAuthorityName="Brancsik" baseAuthorityYear="1888" box="[997,1142,1086,1113]" class="Gastropoda" family="Hydrobiidae" genus="Sarajana" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="apfelbecki">
<emphasis id="B910CB57FFF8FFF1FC331813FB8BDB7A" box="[997,1142,1086,1113]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">S. apfelbecki</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was classified within the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C646CC6FFF8FFF1FF35184EFE80DB5E" authorityName="A. J. Wagner" authorityYear="1928" box="[227,381,1122,1148]" class="Gastropoda" family="Hydrobiidae" genus="Belgrandiella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B910CB57FFF8FFF1FF35184EFE80DB5E" box="[227,381,1122,1148]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Belgrandiella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF56AB4FFF8FFF1FE58184EFD78DB5E" author="Hofman, S. &amp; Osikowski, A. &amp; Rysiewska, A. &amp; Grego, J. &amp; Gloeer, P. &amp; Dmitrovic, D. &amp; Falniowski, A." box="[398,645,1122,1148]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" pagination="407 - 418" refId="ref47772" refString="Hofman, S., Osikowski, A., Rysiewska, A., Grego, J., Gloeer, P., Dmitrovic, D. &amp; Falniowski, A. (2019) Sarajana Radoman, 1975 (Caenogastropoda: Truncatelloidea): premature invalidation of a genus. Journal of Conchology, 43 (4), 407 - 418." type="journal article" year="2019">
Hofman 
<emphasis id="B910CB57FFF8FFF1FE22184FFDCDDB5E" box="[500,560,1122,1148]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">et al.</emphasis>
(2019)
</bibRefCitation>
have showed that based on both, morphological and genetical data, 
<taxonomicName id="4C646CC6FFF8FFF1FF4118ABFF03DB83" authorityName="Radoman" authorityYear="1975" box="[151,254,1159,1185]" class="Gastropoda" family="Hydrobiidae" genus="Sarajana" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B910CB57FFF8FFF1FF4118ABFF03DB83" box="[151,254,1159,1185]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Sarajana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has no close relations to 
<taxonomicName id="4C646CC6FFF8FFF1FDCF18AAFD4EDB82" authorityName="A. J. Wagner" authorityYear="1928" box="[537,691,1158,1184]" class="Gastropoda" family="Hydrobiidae" genus="Belgrandiella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Littorinimorpha" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B910CB57FFF8FFF1FDCF18AAFD4EDB82" box="[537,691,1158,1184]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Belgrandiella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, thus restoring its previous status established by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF56AB4FFF8FFF1FB0E18AAFA64DB82" author="Radoman, P." box="[1240,1433,1158,1184]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" refId="ref53872" refString="Radoman, P. (1983) Hydrobioidea a superfamily of Prosobranchia. Sistematics. Vol. 57. Serbian Academy of Sciences and Arts, Belgrade, 256 pp." type="book" year="1983">Radoman (1983)</bibRefCitation>
. On the IUCN Red List of threatened species it has been assessed as DD (Seddon, 2010). The species is protected on national level (Annex 1-strictly protected species; Official Gazette of 
<collectingRegion id="49A0D9A7FFF8FFF1FC7218E2FC3BDBCA" box="[932,966,1230,1256]" country="Bulgaria" name="Ruse" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">RS</collectingRegion>
5/2010, 47/2011, 32/2016, 98/2016).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BDB1745FFF8FFF1FF411916FDD9DA76" blockId="17.[151,548,1338,1364]" box="[151,548,1338,1364]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
